data.description: Come check out this beautiful townhouse conveniently located between Snellville and Loganville. This nearly new, end-unit is perfect for your future home! With its spacious layout and modern features, this home offers a comfortable and stylish living experience. You are greeted with a stunning stone exterior and cozy entryway. As you enter, the main level opens up to a spacious and inviting living area featuring 9' ceilings and tons of natural light. The open concept design seamingly integrates the kitchen, dining and living area.The kitchen boasts a large center island with beautiful granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, you'll find 2 large secondary bedrooms and an oversized owner's suite perfect for a private retreat. The ensuite offers a generously sized shower with dual vanities and a large walk-in closet. Conveniently located near US-78 with access to great shopping and lots of dining options. Don't miss out on this home! Schedule a tour TODAY! Seller willing to negotiate closing cost contribution with approved offer. Broker bonus and seller incentives available if able to close by 12/17.
